    T\left(\left[\begin{array}{c}0\\0\\1\end{array}\right]\right)
      \not=
    T\left(\left[\begin{array}{c}0\\0\\2\end{array}\right]\right)
  </m>.
    </p>
</li>
<li>
    <p>
    No, because 
  <m>
    T\left(\left[\begin{array}{c}0\\0\\1\end{array}\right]\right)
      =
    T\left(\left[\begin{array}{c}0\\0\\2\end{array}\right]\right)
  </m>.
    </p>
</li>
</ol>
    </statement>
</activity>

